		<!-- message -->
		<div>A lot of the popular SpyWare removal tools don't catch all instances of CoolWebSearch (yet another browser redirection plague).  I run <a href="http://www.spychecker.com/program/cwshredder.html" target="_blank">Cool Web Shredder</a> after Ad-Aware and SpyBot Search &amp; Destroy.<br />
